sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as Envoy Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant BBR as BBR ext-proc<br/>9004/TCP gRPC TLS
    participant EPP as EPP ext-proc<br/>9002/TCP gRPC TLS
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant ModelPod as Model Server Pod<br/>(vLLM / SGLang)
    participant LPTrain as Latency Predictor<br/>Training 8000/TCP
    participant LPPredict as Latency Predictor<br/>Prediction 8000/TCP

    Note over Client,ModelPod: Flow 1: Direct Inference Request Routing (EPP Only)
    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>Auth: Bearer Token / API Key
    Gateway->>EPP: ext-proc ProcessingRequest<br/>gRPC streaming (TLS)
    EPP->>K8sAPI: Watch InferencePool, Pods<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    EPP->>ModelPod: Scrape /metrics<br/>HTTP (KV cache, queue depth)
    Note right of EPP: Filter → Score → Pick<br/>KV-cache score (w=2.0)<br/>Queue depth score (w=2.0)<br/>Prefix cache score (w=3.0)
    EPP-->>Gateway: ProcessingResponse<br/>endpoint selection + headers
    Gateway->>ModelPod: Forward to selected pod<br/>HTTP/8000
    ModelPod-->>Gateway: Inference Response
    Gateway-->>Client: JSON Response

    Note over Client,ModelPod: Flow 2: Body-Based Routing (BBR + EPP)
    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>{"model": "llama-3-70b-lora-a"}
    Gateway->>BBR: ext-proc ProcessingRequest<br/>gRPC streaming (TLS)
    BBR->>K8sAPI: Watch ConfigMaps<br/>(LoRA adapter mappings)
    Note right of BBR: Parse body → extract model name<br/>Resolve LoRA → base model
    BBR-->>Gateway: ProcessingResponse<br/>X-Gateway-Model-Name header<br/>X-Gateway-Base-Model-Name header
    Gateway->>EPP: ext-proc ProcessingRequest<br/>with model name headers
    Note right of EPP: Filter by model availability<br/>Score by metrics + LoRA affinity
    EPP-->>Gateway: ProcessingResponse<br/>endpoint selection
    Gateway->>ModelPod: Forward to selected pod<br/>HTTP/8000
    ModelPod-->>Gateway: Inference Response
    Gateway-->>Client: JSON Response

    Note over EPP,LPPredict: Flow 3: Latency-Aware Scheduling (Optional)
    EPP->>LPTrain: POST /train<br/>Observed TTFT/TPOT data<br/>HTTP/8000
    LPTrain-->>EPP: Model coefficients<br/>Bayesian Ridge / XGBoost
    EPP->>LPPredict: POST /predict/bulk<br/>Current state features<br/>HTTP/8000
    LPPredict-->>EPP: TTFT/TPOT predictions<br/>with uncertainty bounds
    Note right of EPP: Incorporates latency<br/>predictions into scoring
